@startuml saga_pattern_diagram

title BTG Desafio - Saga de Exclusão de Cliente (Choreography-based)

actor Cliente

participant "API Gateway\n:8082" as gateway
participant "Customer Service\n(ms-customer)" as customer
participant "customer.exchange" as exchange
participant "customer.queue.deleted\n[durable]" as queue
participant "Order Service\n(via OpenFeign)" as order
database "MySQL 8.4" as db

Cliente -> gateway : DELETE /api/v1/customer/{id}
gateway -> customer : DELETE /api/v1/customer/{id}
customer -> exchange : publica DefaultEvent(id)\n(routing key: customer.deleted)
customer --> gateway : 202 Accepted

activate queue
exchange -> queue : entrega mensagem

activate customer
queue -> customer : @RabbitListener\nhandleCustomerDeleted(DefaultEvent)

note right of customer
    Saga de compensação:
    antes de remover o cliente,
    remove todos os seus pedidos.
end note

customer -> order : [OpenFeign]\nDELETE /api/v1/order/customer/{id}
order -> db : DELETE order_items WHERE order_id IN (...)\nDELETE orders WHERE customer_id = {id}
order --> customer : 204 No Content

customer -> db : DELETE customers WHERE id = {id}
deactivate customer
deactivate queue

note right of db
    Padrão Saga coreografado:
    Não há orquestrador central.
    O evento customer.deleted aciona
    a compensação (remoção dos pedidos)
    antes da remoção do próprio cliente.
    Comunicação order ← customer via OpenFeign.
end note

@enduml